BEGIN_PGML

[@ image("UBC-CIR-18-562.png", width=>[$width], height=>[$height]) @]*

For the given circuit, [`R_D = 10000`] [`\Omega`], [`R_{G1} = [$rg1]`] [`\Omega`], [`R_{G2} = [$rg2]`] [`\Omega`], [`r_o = 400`] [`k\Omega`], and [`g_m = 8`] [`mS`]. Solve for [`\frac{Vo}{Vs}`].

[`\frac{Vo}{Vs}=`] [_____]{"$gain"}  

END_PGML

